sentences: Adam Svatoš (born June 16, 1979 Prague), known by his stage names MC Kato and Deph, is a Czech rapper, singer, songwriter, record producer and DJ.
As a member of rap duo Flavamatic, he began working with Chaozz in 1994 and later became the main figure in the band.
